{"tid":1808305,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【學界奇聞】期末考前集體「拜楊冪」！ 清華大學生求「大伯」手下留情","createTime":"2020-01-02T09:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T10:05:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85a532ec6753e8a433603a02ab073cdf17167898","tid":1808305,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"在內地，臨到學期尾，總有學生要「臨急抱佛腳」，膜拜孔子、文昌君等各方「大神」，北京清華大學的學生卻與眾不同，他們拜的竟是女星楊冪！<br />\n<br />\n近日有內地網民發文指，他以為清大學生在期末拜楊冪的消息是開玩笑的，沒想到竟是真的！清華大學的微博近日也更新動態，「清華的考試周，楊冪成了微信頭像爆款」、「有冪冪加持，考試必過」，還有人表示，若虔誠的話，期末考前一周就會把大頭貼都換成楊冪的照片，讓人相當好奇為甚麼期末考到了要拜楊冪呢？<br />\n<br />\n原來是因為楊冪的大伯楊曉京是清大數學系教授，同學們把楊冪當成神來拜，為的就是希望大伯能在期末考手下留情，讓他們能順利通過考試。據了解，拜楊冪已經是清大的傳統，多年前楊冪的爸爸也曾在微博提及。<br />\n<br />\n但楊曉京接受媒體採訪時卻笑說：「當然沒用！既沒有理論意義，又沒有實際意義。」他還毫不留情地吐槽親姪女：「楊冪她根本就不懂數學！」網民看完不禁大笑，紛紛留言：「清華學生還是自求多福吧」、「不如直接拜大伯！」<br />\n<br />\n對於大伯吐槽「不懂數學」這一點，其實楊冪早就自嘲過。她曾在訪問中坦承自己一上數學課就頭暈，還跟媽媽撒嬌說自己缺氧了，於是媽媽就給她抱來氧氣罐，楊冪一邊吸氧一邊寫數學作業&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n據悉，早在兩年前，楊曉京就在網上走紅了，除了因為他是楊冪的大伯外，還因為他熱衷健身、擁有一身肌肉，特別愛穿緊身衣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200101/large/1577888102_b331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200101%2Flarge%2F1577888102_b331.jpg&h=13754cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200102/60439447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60439447&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPm1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=8734aaa3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60439447&h=a3384b51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200102/60439447</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚on 9  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ac352f6789f92c5eed23e26c7aeeb10168de6e","tid":1808305,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"低賤"},{"pid":"fb02cea986b06e462a1ceea1fe68514eef590492","tid":1808305,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"我老公呢"},{"pid":"518f5c4860e32556e1668eb07c37d3e8c38613d0","tid":1808305,"uid":73598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"我有老公！"},{"pid":"d47a9dfb81515b55b5923fcbd58067e56bef3414","tid":1808305,"uid":50428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"我考physics 都拜福山雅治啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c3b3e6c887a641e515a227b62f6e9d3ba5b6fb","tid":1808305,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb02cea986b06e462a1ceea1fe68514eef590492","tid":1808305,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"我老公呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯嗯嗯"}]}